result.title: Fun SRM / Pittsburgh regional round
result.content: I see that in 2,5 hours there is a fun SRM, so I thought I would let you know cause I learned that coincidentally and I see no blog about it (but expect it to be probably significantly easier than Div 1 :( ). If I did everything correctly, here is its time: https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?msg=Fun+SRM+%28Pittsburgh%29&iso=20170908T19&ah=1&am=35 P.S. clist.by shows this: https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?msg=TCO17%20Pittsburgh%20Event%20/%20Fun%20SRM&iso=20170908T1700&ah=6&am=0 which is 2 hours earlier, but Arena's schedule says what is in first link...
